# Web Rules (Map Frontend)

## Purpose
Public map website using MapLibre.

## Responsibilities
- Render map using tiles
- Display POIs and search results
- Handle user interactions

## Data Sources
- Tiles (PMTiles / Martin) → map rendering
- API → search and place details

## Rules
- Do NOT connect to database
- Do NOT implement business logic
- Keep UI lightweight

## Map Rules
- Use MapLibre GL JS
- Load style.json from tiles/styles
- Keep layers minimal for performance

## API Usage
- Fetch search results from API
- Fetch place details from API

## Performance
- Optimize rendering
- Avoid unnecessary layers
- Keep bundle small

## Forbidden
- Heavy logic
- Direct DB access
- Tile generation